I have such a strange feeling that for the last month I have been living inside an incessant party in a dope. Game is going on around, sometimes even something encouraging happens, but it is immediately blocked by portions of new game. Nichrome is not clear, in some places it is interesting, in more places it is scary. Someone is neighing, someone is yelling, someone is crying somewhere, orderlies are running everywhere, a pipe has burst on the floor above, someone is hammering on the radiator in the next room, somewhere further down the corridor a group is singing hymns ...